# EDARS Enhancement Plan — Enterprise-Grade Upgrade

## Overview
Comprehensive enhancement of the EDARS platform with production-grade infrastructure additions.

## Enhancements

### 1. Gateway — Threat Intelligence Middleware (`threatIntel.js`)
- Automated IP reputation scoring
- Geo-fencing with configurable country block/allow lists
- Request fingerprinting (TLS fingerprint, header ordering)
- Honeypot trap endpoints that flag bad actors
- Auto-escalating ban system (warn → throttle → temporary ban → permanent ban)

### 2. Gateway — Cryptographic Request Signing (`hmacVerify.js`)
- HMAC-SHA256 request signing for all API calls
- Timestamp-based replay attack prevention (5-minute window)
- Nonce tracking via Redis to prevent duplicate requests
- Constant-time comparison to prevent timing attacks

### 3. Gateway — Enhanced Observability (`metrics.js`)
- Prometheus-compatible metrics endpoint
- Request latency histograms (p50, p95, p99)
- Error rate counters by route
- Active connection gauge
- Circuit breaker state metrics
- Memory and event loop utilisation

### 4. Analytics — Predictive Intelligence (`forecasting.py`)
- Time-series forecasting using linear regression + seasonal decomposition
- Revenue prediction per department (30/60/90 day)
- Anomaly severity scoring with confidence intervals
- Pattern detection for spending trends

### 5. Analytics — Data Pipeline Engine (`pipeline.py`)
- ETL pipeline framework for scheduled data processing
- Aggregation jobs with checkpointing
- Incremental processing with watermark tracking
- Dead-letter queue for failed pipeline stages

### 6. Database — Security Hardening (`005_security_hardening.sql`)
- Column-level encryption functions using pgcrypto
- Data masking views for PII fields
- Failed login tracking table with automatic IP blocking triggers
- Session management table with device fingerprinting
- Cryptographic hash chain for audit log integrity verification

### 7. Infrastructure — Docker Compose Enhancements
- Add Prometheus + Alertmanager containers
- Resource limit tuning
- Healthcheck improvements

### 8. Environment/Config Enhancements
- New security-related env vars
- HMAC signing keys
- Geo-fence config
- Metrics toggle
